PrecisAppointment of ARTHUR GOBEIL of Saguenay, Quebec, to be a director of the Saguenay Port Authority, to hold office for a term of two years, effective December 11, 2018, in the place of Martial Bouchard, whose term expired on March 6, 2016, but continues in office until December 10, 2018.
